}{}$${\rm{GSS}} = {{\sum\nolimits_{(i = 1)}^n {{\rm{compScor}}{{\rm{e}}_i}} } \over {\sum\nolimits_{(i = 1)}^n {{\rm{selfScor}}{{\rm{e}}_i}} }}.$$\end{document}GSS=∑(i=1)ncompScorei∑(i=1)nselfScorei.
